{"tid":611572,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼佬utuber介紹過百種捉老鼠工具","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T10:44:29.000Z","uid":33875,"like":114,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c374be65238c3222790ef7c809167055e9a6bf6e","tid":611572,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yt3.ggpht.com/-cjmvuzm6Mx8/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/eYbB0CEXBS8/s288-mo-c-c0xffffffff-rj-k-no/photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyt3.ggpht.com%2F-cjmvuzm6Mx8%2FAAAAAAAAAAI%2FAAAAAAAAAAA%2FeYbB0CEXBS8%2Fs288-mo-c-c0xffffffff-rj-k-no%2Fphoto.jpg&h=8735fe5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/historichunter/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fhistorichunter%2Fvideos&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=10ed468d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/historichunter/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n幾年前個channel都係正正常常教下野外捕獵技巧，捕獵就好自然要整陷阱去捉獵物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一日佢發現自己屋企好多老鼠，就整個陷阱捉埋佢地，搞搞下佢開始發現自己整既老鼠夾幾受歡迎，放上ebay仲有唔少人訂購，本來間中拍一兩條，最近幾乎主力玩老鼠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十八世紀流行既老鼠鐵網箱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SL2HrHH_Pas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSL2HrHH_Pas&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d74fac0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SL2HrHH_Pas</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144609_fb6973705cee3ccc9f4afbcb50ba895c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144609_fb6973705cee3ccc9f4afbcb50ba895c.png&h=0a66fa73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有重製400年前既吊頸式老鼠夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wvWD-E-gbkk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwvWD-E-gbkk&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=840bfe3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wvWD-E-gbkk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144038_cbc067631f52ea33d0180b2f2ba14405.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144038_cbc067631f52ea33d0180b2f2ba14405.png&h=3161f267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得另一大特色既實戰片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144117_7b47d90124a63f2e36e8ca9e9e7ba988.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144117_7b47d90124a63f2e36e8ca9e9e7ba988.png&h=e2b4319d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結合新科技3D打印版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J-Mr69zlbys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ-Mr69zlbys&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1797f428\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J-Mr69zlbys</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144734_80c051681c3cf23a1a86f712b910df35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144734_80c051681c3cf23a1a86f712b910df35.png&h=3f3d7c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144735_e73405f76eed9d731e472725f324147f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144735_e73405f76eed9d731e472725f324147f.png&h=c439a51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLego版呢個真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IF3AMENXTfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIF3AMENXTfE&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2d4821fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IF3AMENXTfE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144914_9218dc7e30f03ccb9f96ebfa6de234b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144914_9218dc7e30f03ccb9f96ebfa6de234b8.png&h=4d2cf878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/144914_f67ff465ae3646ad9359e8ee20f5bb24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F144914_f67ff465ae3646ad9359e8ee20f5bb24.png&h=b72dee5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個好似過份左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oM09ZgY2qPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoM09ZgY2qPM&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=895cddae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oM09ZgY2qPM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/145115_d84b0d507c24fed0552791d7d21342b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F145115_d84b0d507c24fed0552791d7d21342b7.png&h=8e403a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/145116_ec21f7842ed